QuestData.Title: Sea Slug Liquidation
QuestData.Description:
My brief studies have shown that the refinement process creates a byproduct that is invisible to the naked eye, but is easily seen with refracted bioluminescent light.
The sea floor is littered with creatures that produce just what we need to track down this weapons cache.
QuestData.LogDescription: Collect $1oa Bioluminescent Ooze from Luminescent Sea Slugs within Bloodfin Village.
